    "See chat log: https://chat.openai.com/share/ff1d00b7-69aa-4f9d-a92e-a88236701db7. et al.",
    "10.3389/feduc.2024.1417900 Frontiers in Education 13 frontiersin.org",
    "Secondly, the experiment illustrates that the risks arising from faulty syntax generated by GPT software are manageable, as its use is not possible, thereby preventing (presumed incorrect) results from being produced.",
    "Again, the greater risk lies in user-based decision-making based on the proposed solution options.",
    "Thirdly, while some literature supports the claim that using AI support for specific tasks can save time, the experiment shows that this is also tied to the knowledge of the user and their ability to adapt to the particularities of the tool -in our chase GPT 3.5."
